com.mcc.ul
Class AiCalConfig

java.lang.Object
  com.mcc.ul.AiCalConfig

public class AiCalConfig
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods to get or set calibration settings of an analog input subsystem on a DAQ device. To create an instance of this class, call the getCalConfig() method of the AiConfig class.
